每群裸鼹鼠有一只相当肥硕的王后和几只雄鼠，其余无论雌雄均为工鼠，工鼠可能受王后尿中外激素的抑制而失去了[[生殖能力|生殖能力]]，专门负责采集食物、为王后保温、挖掘[[隧道|隧道]]等。一窝裸鼹鼠平均有七八十只，最多能达300只，但是每只工鼠的体重大约只有30克<ref>陈阅增《普通生物学》第四版P337</ref>。

==特殊能力==
牠們特殊的身體機能令其可在惡劣的地下环境裡繁衍，包括<ref name=ettoday>{{cite news |url=http://www.ettoday.net/news/20120908/99950.htm#ixzz2cSJk5zvw |title=不老「裸鼠」皺巴巴　暗藏人類長壽密碼 |publisher=[[ETtoday|ETtoday]]新奇新聞 |language=zh-hant |date=2012-09-08 |accessdate=2013-08-19 |archive-date=2013-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130720100402/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20120908/99950.htm#ixzz2cSJk5zvw |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=dailymail>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-2198650/This-naked-mole-rat-hold-secret-humans-living-200-hopefully-wrinkles.html |title=The 'naked mole rat' that could hold the secret to humans living to 200 (...although hopefully without the wrinkles) |author=Eddie Wrenn |date=2012-09-05 |accessdate=2013-08-19 |language=en |archive-date=2014-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140119072458/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-2198650/This-naked-mole-rat-hold-secret-humans-living-200-hopefully-wrinkles.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>：
*皮肤[[痛觉|痛觉]]的缺失；
*非常低的[[代谢|代谢]]率，使牠可以有一般老鼠長10倍的30年壽命；
*[[哺乳類|哺乳類]]動物當中唯一具備[[體溫調節|體溫調節]]功能的冷血物種<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.livescience.com/16516-naked-mole-rat-genome-longevity.html |title=Naked Mole Rat Genome May Hold Key to Long Life | Human Health & Longevity | Cancer Resistance & Naked Mole Rat |publisher=LiveScience |date=2011-10-12 |accessdate=2013-03-23 |archive-date=2013-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130402221805/http://www.livescience.com/16516-naked-mole-rat-genome-longevity.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，使之能夠承受異常高溫；
*身體機能幾乎不會退化；
*癌症發病幾率很低；
*到死前都可以繁殖後代；
*不怕吃到有毒植物；
*沒有氧氣也能存活一段時間<ref>{{cite news |url=http://science.sciencemag.org/content/356/6335/307 |title=Fructose-driven glycolysis supports anoxia resistance in the naked mole-rat |publisher=Science |date=2017-04-21 |accessdate=2017-04-24 |archive-date=2017-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170424021835/http://science.sciencemag.org/content/356/6335/307 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*隨年齡增長，[[死亡率|死亡率]]低於其他哺乳動物<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=55365 |title=裸鼴鼠不會衰老 |accessdate=2018-01-28 |archive-date=2018-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180128132709/https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=55365 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

由於裸鼹鼠與人類基因的DNA有高達80%到93%相同，英國[[牛津大學|牛津大學]]的科學家認為裸鼹鼠的長壽秘密應該同樣可應用到人體，令人類延壽至200歲<ref name=ettoday /><ref name=dailymail />。

